<h3> <a name="Development"></a><font face="Arial,Helvetica">Development</font></h3>
<blockquote>OpenSLP is a continuation of an SLP implementation started
at Caldera Systems, Inc.&nbsp; The current (1.2.x) version is
considered stable and usable in production applications.&nbsp;
The CVS repository has now been branched for more agressive development so that
new features can be added (see the <a href="roadmap.html">Roadmap</a>
for details).
  <p>If you are interested in working on OpenSLP please look at the
1.3.x releases. </p>
  <p>The following links provide additional information: </p>
  <ul>
    <li> <a href="ports.html">Ports</a></li>
    <li> <a href="cvs.html">CVS Access</a></li>
    <li> <a href="roadmap.html">Development Roadmap</a></li>
    <li> <a href="http://sourceforge.net/project/?group_id=1730">Group
page on SourceForge</a></li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>
